ActBank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Finance of ERNEST DANIELS of West Kelowna, British Columbia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Bank of Canada, to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending on February 28, 2026, effective March 1, 2023.
